pnpm install
pnpm build          # Should produce dist/index.js, dist/index.mjs, dist/index.d.ts
pnpm type-check     # Should pass with no TypeScript errors

# From workspace root
pnpm type-check:full   # Confirm no cross-package type errors
```

Smoke test usage pattern:
```typescript
